</p>
			</div>
		</div></li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px"><div style="width: 155px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 150px;"><div style="margin:43.5px auto;"><a href="/wiki/File:RutilusRutilusScalesLateralLine.JPG" class="image" title="Cycloid scales on a common roach (Rutilus rutilus)"><img alt="Cycloid scales on a common roach (Rutilus rutilus)" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e9/RutilusRutilusScalesLateralLine.JPG/120px-RutilusRutilusScalesLateralLine.JPG" decoding="async" width="120" height="63" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e9/RutilusRutilusScalesLateralLine.JPG/180px-RutilusRutilusScalesLateralLine.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e9/RutilusRutilusScalesLateralLine.JPG/240px-RutilusRutilusScalesLateralLine.JPG 2x" data-file-width="942" data-file-height="495" /></a></div></div>
